      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.archetypes.qFvDAPc7jHZvFgy1]{Starfinder Forerunner}</p>\n<p>You’ve spent enough time in strange lands, far from the safety of known civilization, to learn to patch up technology and vehicles—and even yourself and fellow travelers—using whatever is at hand. Once per day as a standard action, you can spend 1 Resolve Point to regain a number of Stamina Points equal to your class level (up to your maximum). Alternatively, you can take 10 minutes and spend 1 Resolve Point to restore Hit Points equal to your class level to one vehicle, piece of equipment, or creature. It is assumed you have gathered whatever materials you need to perform this action in your normal activities.</p>"
